data.description: Welcome home to 10 Del Rancho Lane located in the sought after Granada Country Estates.  With almost 5000 square feet of living space & 3.62 acres, there is LOTS of room inside & outside.  As you enter the home you are welcomed by beautiful wood floors, large windows over looking the dreamy pool, and a kitchen made for a chef.  The living room is open to the dining room, eat in and kitchen.  In the kitchen you will find Thermador appliances, sub zero fridge, a prep sink in the island and heated marble floors.  The master suite is a dream of its own!  Very spacious with access to the back patio area.  The master bath has a large walk in shower, soaking tub and double vanities.  The secondary bedrooms are located on the other side of the home & joined by a jack-n-jill bath.  Upstairs is the bonus room with a fireplace and built in bar area.  It can also be used as a bedroom with the access to a closet and bathroom.  Off the garage is an extra room for hobbies, work out room, or a second office.  The detached 2 car shop holds the pool equipment and is equipped with air lines throughout for the car lover.  Above the shop is a 400 square foot studio apartment with a kitchenette, walk in closet and bathroom.  And last but not least, the pool and hot tub!  With a gorgeous waterfall, this is the perfect place to entertain friends and family all summer long!  All of this sits on 3.62 acres and ready for its new family!
